<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <style>
    body { font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; background-color: #f6f9fc; color: #333; margin: 0; padding: 20px; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background: white; padding: 30px; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.05); }
    .logo { color: #1a56db; font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 20px; text-decoration: none; }
    .btn { display: inline-block; background-color: #1a56db; color: white !important; font-weight: 500; font-size: 16px; padding: 12px 24px; border-radius: 6px; text-decoration: none; margin-top: 20px; }
    .footer { font-size: 12px; color: #888; margin-top: 30px; text-align: center; border-top: 1px solid #eaeaea; padding-top: 20px; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 20px;">
      <img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dlfzzfdx0/image/upload/v1777286182/Brand_title_with_tagline-removebg-preview_jpjpet.png" alt="Proteccio Data" style="width: 200px; height: auto; margin-bottom: 5px;">
      <p style="color:#2ecc71; margin:0; font-size:10px; letter-spacing:1px; font-weight: bold; text-transform: uppercase;">
          Data Privacy • Compliance • Implementation
      </p>
    </div>
    
    <h2 style="color: #111827; margin-top: 0;">You've been invited!</h2>
    
    <p>Hi there,</p>
    <p>You have been invited to join the <strong>Consent Management System</strong> ecosystem by an administrator.</p>
    
    {{#if role}}
    <p><strong>Assigned Role:</strong> {{role}}</p>
    {{/if}}

    <p>Click the button below to accept the invitation and set up your account. This link will expire in exactly 48 hours.</p>

    <a href="{{inviteUrl}}" class="btn">Accept Invitation</a>

    <p style="margin-top: 30px;">If this wasn't you or you believe this was sent by mistake, please ignore this email or contact support.</p>

    <div class="footer">
      &copy; {{year}} Proteccio Data Privacy. All rights reserved.
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
